summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to Land Use and Zoning; amending Plat 305E, Page 190 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone property located at 10020 Martin Luther King Jr. Way south from Residential Single Family (SF 7200) to General Industrial (IG) Zone and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Dave Scheiber; C.F. 293518).
